title: The Cat in the Hat Knows a Lot About That! Season 2, Eps 19-20
description:
Here they finally are, the last two episodes of Cat in the Hat Knows a lot about that. These last two episodes episodes finally aired in June 2015, and were encoded by me, using recordings from my local PBS station.

There's actually one more episode I need to upload: 2-11. Little Lemmings - Keep The Beat, which apparently was not in the earlier pack like I thought. I will keep an eye out for that one and record it the next time it's on.

If you enjoy this torrent, be sure to leave me a comment! And please continue to leave this seeding in your torrent client after your download completes, so that others can enjoy this great kids educational show. I haven't heard any news that there will be a third season, but if it ever does happen I will be sure to record any new episodes from my local PBS station on digital cable when they are shown, as long as people continue to seed!
